    { "id": 10, "type": "timeseries", "title": "Shadow − live latency delta (p95)", "description": "Positive means the shadow upstream is slower than live at p95 — a candidate performance regression in the new service.", "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" }, "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 16, "x": 0, "y": 24 }, "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "s", "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 10, "gradientMode": "scheme" } }, "overrides": [] }, "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" } }, "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" }, "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le) (rate(http_client_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service=\"mroki-proxy\",mroki_target=\"shadow\"}[5m]))) - histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le) (rate(http_client_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service=\"mroki-proxy\",mroki_target=\"live\"}[5m])))", "legendFormat": "shadow − live p95" } ] },
    { "id": 11, "type": "text", "title": "Blind spot", "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 24 }, "options": { "mode": "markdown", "content": "**Outbound counts only responses received.** Connection failures, timeouts and circuit-breaker-open events are **not** in `http_client_request_duration_seconds` — they surface only in logs (see issue #18). A live/shadow upstream that is *down* shows up as **missing** outbound requests, not as an elevated error ratio." }, "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" } },
